name: Weng Santos
text: That's just not what worries me.  It's a label and I don't roll like that.    I'm more worried that 30 years from now, extra-judicial killings are not just commonplace, but that Duterte has made it the norm, only then they're being shot with AKs, coz you know, Russia.  That we're an annex of China.  That traffic has turned the Philippines into a parking lot.  Or that Bataan turns into Chernobyl disaster and our grand kids are born with 5 eyes and 6 legs.    I guess I jus't don't feel strongly about what people say the burial means like you guys do.
